## Project
This is Zevian â€” an AI-powered B2B SaaS performance management tool.
Dark theme. Target: remote team managers. Markets: EU and US.

## Design System Location
All design tokens, atoms, and molecules live in `src/` of this package.
The barrel export is at `src/index.ts`.
Import path alias: `@/design-system`

NEVER hardcode colors, font names, sizes, spacing, or border-radius values.
ALWAYS import from `@/design-system`.

## Typography Rules
- Headings, scores, logo: `typography.fonts.display` â†’ Syne, fontWeight 700â€“800
- All UI body text: `typography.fonts.body` â†’ DM Sans
- Numbers, weights, percentages, monospace data: `typography.fonts.mono` â†’ DM Mono

## Color Rules
- Page backgrounds: `colors.bg` (#0a0c10)
- Card/sidebar/header surfaces: `colors.surface` (#111318)
- Nested elements, inputs, hover backgrounds: `colors.surface2` (#181c24)
- Deepest nesting, score bar tracks, skeletons: `colors.surface3` (#1e2330)
- Primary brand: `colors.accent` (#5b7fff)
- AI/teal accent: `colors.teal` (#00d4aa)
- Score colors: ALWAYS use `getScoreColor(score)` â€” never hardcode
  - â‰Ą 7.5 â†’ green (#10b981)
  - 6.0â€“7.4 â†’ warn (#f59e0b)
  - < 6.0 â†’ danger (#f04438)

## Component Rules
- Scores: always `<Score value={x} size="sm|md|lg|xl" />`
- Status: always `<StatusPill status="on-track|at-risk|review|overdue|no-reports" />`
- Tags/chips: always `<Chip variant="muted|blue|green|amber|red|teal|purple">`
- Avatars: `<Avatar name="..." />` or `<AvatarStack names={[...]} max={3} />`
- Buttons: `<Button variant="primary|secondary|ghost|danger" size="sm|md|lg|icon">`
- Inputs: `<Input label="..." required />`, `<Textarea />`, `<Select options={[...]} />`
- Modals: RIGHT-SIDE SHEET only. Use `<Modal>` with sticky header + footer
- Cards: outer = `<Card>` (borderRadius 14px), inner = `<NestedCard>` (borderRadius 10px)

## Layout Rules
- Sidebar width: `layout.sidebarWidth` = 220px (var(--sidebar-width))
- Header height: `layout.headerHeight` = 56px (var(--header-height))
- Content padding: 28px
- Main content: `marginLeft: layout.sidebarWidth`, `paddingTop: layout.headerHeight`

## Animation Rules
- All hover transitions: `animation.fast` = 0.15s ease
- Card entrance: `animate-fade-up` CSS class (defined in global.css)
- Sheet slide-in: `animate-slide-in` CSS class
- Empty state icon: `pulse-ring` CSS class
- Score bar fill: `bar-animate` CSS class

## File Locations
- Design tokens:     src/design/tokens.ts
- Global CSS:        src/design/global.css
- Atoms:             src/components/atoms/
- Molecules:         src/components/molecules/
- Barrel export:     src/index.ts
- Cursor prompts:    CURSOR_PROMPTS.md

## What NOT to do
- Do not use Bootstrap, MUI, Ant Design, or any third-party component library
- Do not use Tailwind utility classes for colors (use tokens instead)
- Do not use purple gradients on white backgrounds
- Do not use Inter, Roboto, or Arial fonts
- Do not create centered dialog modals â€” always use right-side sheets
- Do not hardcode score colors â€” use getScoreColor()
- Do not create new status pill designs â€” use <StatusPill>
